Program: Outlook
Title: Organ Donation
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrg4
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Organ donations and the case of 6 year old Sally Slater who needed a heart transplant operation. Also, Restaurateur Mourad Mazouz talks about his favourite meal; A visit to Moluccan immigrants in Amsterdam. Finally, interesting smells and flavours from Marseille, France. Presenter: Frederick Dove.